snippet.title: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes Video Game - Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Your favorite heroes, including Iron Man, Wolverine, Spider-Man, Hulk, Thor and more, assemble for "LEGO Marvel Super Heroes," coming to all major consoles this fall!
